{
  "texts": [
    "Some themes do not have enough data to support them or the data are too diverse (Braun and Clarke 2006).",
    "Also, generative AI (van Dis et al. 2023) was not much hyped during the sampling process.",
    "These topics are missing and call for further research to understand the field from more diverse perspectives, disciplines and expertise.",
    "Unexpectedly, the participants rarely mentioned certain fundamental topics of the field, such as platformization, the Metaverse, mixed realities, machine learning, sentient technologies, and more.",
    "Possible reasons for this could be that (1) these are not necessarily the future which they expect, (2) they do not use these applications regularly, or (3) they are unaware of the black box technology behind these services."
  ]
}